{"type": "article", "id": 24279, "title": "墨尔本的这个阁楼式公寓曲线夸张，就连家具都很怪趣味", "description": "楼梯是焦点。", "date": "2016-03-23T10:39:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 14006, "name": "住宅设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702123217daYzRefBKCHZVI52.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>初看墨尔本这座公寓，我猜想屋主人一定是个有点怪趣味的人。</p>\n<p>这是墨尔本当地的 <a href=\"http://www.aaarchitects.com.au/index.php?/projectslist/west-melbourne/\">Adrian Amore 建筑事务所</a>的新作 Loft Apartment，三层阁楼式的结构给予了他们充分的设计改造想象力。</p>\n<p>先来看看这个实在太过引人注目的空间结构，单一白色的石膏墙体结构好似不规则伸展一般自地面层向上延伸，形成了曲线夸张的楼梯造型和整个空间的墙体，它看似扭曲，却又是流畅的线条，较之于建筑结构，说实话它更像是一个艺术装置。</p>\n<p>很少会有人在家居空间中尝试这般大胆的做法。</p>\n<p>流线型的墙体把公寓完全敞开式的平面空间分割为一个个相对私密的区域。</p>\n<p>一层通往二层、二层通向阁楼的楼梯造型，成为整个屋子的视觉焦点，支撑楼梯的黑色钢柱和纯黑色的台阶与白色石膏墙体形成强烈反差，黑白色调的组合给屋子增添了一点酷酷的劲儿。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123211oMShtGjO1VWI2xHd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123212KqXCrDicsxz3aWvY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123212o8RtPWsCKIBTzlFm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123213iW2wtb4k8YgTsZ3Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>如果家中有客人来访，一进入到起居室便能感受到充满戏剧性的氛围。大面积的钢质窗格将自然光线引入室内，遇上个好天气的话，白色空间会显得更加通透。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021232131zdx9eBKL7cPSQv5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123213BxwS2pmjNOtJL8Za.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96385542\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123214u58frWaMhO79loKs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.427\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>除了硬装外，Loft Apartment 的软装也很有趣，从家具的选择便能看出屋主人的爱好。</p>\n<p>线条利落的灰色沙发很有几何感，与黑白空间相搭几乎是不会出错的组合。故意缺了桌面一角的餐桌大理石餐桌很吸睛，造型别致，又与厨房的大理石台面相呼应。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123214G3bPKhu2Q6wtv1fi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.432\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123215Eg70cZR9a4uS2Lvw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0025\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>用木条拼接而成的方方正正的座椅旁，是一款简单的玻璃边几。不多的数十本书就放置在厨房台面上方的平板支架上。</p>\n<p>位于二层的休闲空间中，还藏着一个底座是折叠曲线木板的座椅和一块彩虹拼色款地毯。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123215DnVgbafYsJ6FNlGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123216GkxFumhUviYI3fRg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021232160TKwXUyASO6F1N3j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>大部分区域都空置着，屋主人亦没有想要填满它。一个戏剧性十足的空间加上寥寥几个趣味满分的家具，就是家的全部了。</p>\n<p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.aaarchitects.com.au/index.php?/projectslist/west-melbourne/\">Adrian Amore Architects</a> 摄影：Fraser Marsden</p>\n\n"}